"parametern ``action``) bĂ¶r ha attributen :attr:`!dest`, :attr:`!"
"option_strings`, :attr:`!default`, :attr:`!type`, :attr:`!required`, :attr:`!"
"help`, etc. definierade. Det enklaste sĂ¤ttet att sĂ¤kerstĂ¤lla att dessa "
"attribut Ă¤r definierade Ă¤r att anropa :meth:`!Action.__init__`."

#: ../../library/argparse.rst:1392
msgid ""
":class:`!Action` instances should be callable, so subclasses must override "
