"till :meth:`set_defaults` sĂĄ att varje subparser vet vilken Python-funktion "
"den ska utfĂ¶ra.  Till exempel::"

#: ../../library/argparse.rst:1821
msgid ""
">>> # subcommand functions\n"
">>> def foo(args):\n"
"...     print(args.x * args.y)\n"
