"ett argument per rad. :meth:`convert_arg_line_to_args` kan ĂĄsidosĂ¤ttas fĂ¶r "
"mer avancerad lĂ¤sning."

#: ../../library/argparse.rst:2161
msgid ""
"This method takes a single argument *arg_line* which is a string read from "
"the argument file.  It returns a list of arguments parsed from this string. "
"The method is called once per line read from the argument file, in order."
msgstr ""
"Denna metod tar ett enda argument *arg_line* som Ă¤r en strĂ¤ng som lĂ¤ses frĂĄn "
"argumentfilen.  Den returnerar en lista med argument som tolkats frĂĄn denna "
"strĂ¤ng. Metoden anropas en gĂĄng per rad som lĂ¤ses frĂĄn argumentfilen, i "
"ordning."

#: ../../library/argparse.rst:2165
msgid ""
"A useful override of this method is one that treats each space-separated "
